msgid "Outdated Client version detected!"
msgstr "Bezero bertsio zaharra detektatu da!"

msgid "Do not show again"
msgstr "Ez berriro erakutsi"

msgid "Leave Server"
msgstr "Utzi Zerbitzaria"

msgid "Ignore"
msgstr "Ez kasurik egin"

msgid "You are connecting with an unsupported client. This will generally not keep you from playing the game but you should expect some visual issues, particularly with mobs and certain items.\n"
"\n"
"To enjoy the best mineclonia experience use a minetest/luanti client of version 5.9.0 or greater."
msgstr ""
"Onartuta ez dagoen bezero batekin konektatzen ari zara. Orokorrean jolastu "
"ahal izan beharko zenuke, baina arazo bisual batzuk ikus ditzakezu, batez "
"ere izaki eta objektu batzuekin.\n"
"\n"
"mineclonia-ren esperientzia hoberenaz gozatzeko, erabili minetest/luanti-ren "
"bezeroaren 5.9.9 bertsioa edo berriagoa."
